conductor can be\ntested experimentally through the measurement of the band shift.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Jan 2018 17:52:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Apr 2018 12:49:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-20"}
