ceeds the star formation rate for V_H < 200 km/s and u_0 = 50 km/s, a typical\nfountain velocity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Jan 2018 19:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-28"}
