$, a\nPomeranchuk instability occurs at $F^{c(s)}_{l} =-1$ for an order parameter\nwith any form-factor\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Jan 2018 20:59:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-11"}
